OL,5, Schools are spending tens of thousands 
OL,6, of pounds more a year to meet rising   
OL,7, costs of contracts with private firms. 
OL,9,FThese Private Finance Initiative (PFI) 
OL,10,Fschools are locked into 25- to 30-year 
OL,11,Fcontracts in which charges rise more   
OL,12,Fthan at other schools.                 
OL,14,FOne school said it was spending        
OL,15,Fthousands of pounds a year to keep its 
OL,16,Fplaying-field grass below 2.5cm (1in), 
OL,17,Fas the "rigid" contract demanded.      
OL,19,FPFI investors say the contracts give   
OL,20,Flong-term value for taxpayers' money.  
